  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The country will be in darkness for 3 hours again from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Acting General Manager Engineer Dr.D. C. R. Abeysekera said.",
        "Mr. Abeysekera further said that the second power plant of Norochchole Lakwijaya Power Plant with a capacity of 270 MW is undergoing essential maintenance work, so the power cut has to be increased due to the loss of power capacity of 540 MW.",
        "The chairman of the commission, Mr. Janatha Ratnayake, also said that the Public Utilities Commission approved the three-hour power cut."
      ],
